data.description: Bring a little paint, a vision, and throw in some love to bring this amazing home back to life and add sweat equity in the process! This fantastic home is located in the heart of Omaha with convenient access to everything from shopping, restaurants, Dodge Street, and much more! When you walk in the door your mind will begin to see all the little details that can bring this home back to life. The sprawling floor plan offers abundant space to spread out and the fenced back yard is ready for the summer bbq you have been planning at your new home. Lets bring this home the new owner and life it has been waiting for!
